#### **NFC **

```c
#include <nfc/nfc.h>
int main() {
    
    nfc_context *context = nfc_init(NULL);
    
    nfc_device *device = nfc_open(context, NULL);
    
    nfc_command cmd;
    cmd.ndf_id = 0x01;
    cmd.ndf_len = 0x04;
    cmd.ndf_data = "Hello";
    
    nfc_encrypt_command(device, &cmd);
    
    nfc_send_command(device, &cmd);
    
    nfc_close(device);
    
    nfc_exit(context);
    return 0;
}
```
#### ****

---

- `cmd`:  NFC

```c

#include "stm32f4xx_hal_nfc.h"
int main(void)
{
  
  HAL_Init();
  
  HAL_NFC_Init();
  
  HAL_NFC_Select();
  
  uint8_t data[16];
  HAL_NFC_Read(data, 16);
  
  HAL_NFC_Write(data, 16);
  
  while (1)
  {
  }
}
```
